query:
SELECT
                u.id as user_id,
                u.username,
                u.profile_picture_url
            FROM users u
            WHERE u.status = 'active'
            AND LOWER(u.username) LIKE $1
            ORDER BY
                CASE WHEN LOWER(u.username) = $2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END,
                u.username
            LIMIT $3
